article_id:1564,category_name:News,title_name:Presenting 2nd Anniversary Events!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/bc06ff1e74717475cacdc2c208b180f9.png,message:<div>Events for the second anniversary will start at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601013600"></span>.</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/bc06ff1e74717475cacdc2c208b180f9.png"></div><div><br></div><hr><div>1. Announcing a Platinum Showcase! 5★ Gala Dragalia Adventurer Guaranteed!</div><div>A Platinum Showcase where a 5★ Gala Dragalia adventurer available at the time of this summon showcase is guaranteed to appear in the tenfold summon will be held!</div><div><br></div><div>■Availability Period</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601186400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601877599"></span></div><div><br></div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/1611">See here for more information.</a></div><div><br></div><hr><div>2. Announcing Gala Dragalia!</div><div>The initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers and dragons will be boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%!</div><div><br></div><div>In the Gala Dragalia starting at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601186400"></span>, you can redeem wyrmsigils for any of the Gala Dragalia adventurers and dragons who appeared in Gala Dragalia events until <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601186400"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>■Availability Period</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601186400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601445599"></span></div><div><br></div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/1609">See here for more information.</a></div><div><br></div><div>What&#39;s more, Gala Zena will be the featured adventurer in a Gala Dragalia starting at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601445600"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>■Availability Period</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601445600"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601877599"></span></div><div><br></div><hr><div>3. 2nd Anniversary Packs Are Coming!</div><div>Anniversary packs will be available for a limited time under Value Packs in the Shop starting at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601186400"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>■Availability Period</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601186400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1604037599"></span></div><div><br></div><hr><div>4. Daily Free Tenfold Summon Incoming!</div><div>A daily free tenfold summon event, which will allow you to perform a tenfold summon on the applicable summon showcase for free once per day, starts at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601186400"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601186400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1604037599"></span></div><div><br></div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/1606">See here for more information.</a></div><div><br></div><hr><div>5. 2nd Anniversary Bonus!</div><div>Get the following incredible rewards when you log in during the event duration!</div><div><br></div><div>■Daily Rewards</div><div>Day 1: Champion&#39;s Testament &times; 2</div><div>Day 2: Mini Hildy &times; 1</div><div>Day 3: Talonstone &times; 50</div><div>Day 4: Rainbow Orb &times; 20</div><div>Day 5: Wyrmite &times; 1,000</div><div>Day 6: 5★ wyrmprint &quot;Second Anniversary&quot; &times; 1</div><div>Day 7: 5★ Summon Voucher (Dragon) &times; 1</div><div>Day 8: Damascus Ingot &times; 1</div><div>Day 9: Wyrmite &times; 1,000</div><div>Day 10: Sunlight Stone &times; 1</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601186400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1604037599"></span></div><div><br></div><div>In addition, the following dragons will be added to the fafnir medals section of the Treasure Trade:</div><div>・Mini Mids</div><div>・Mini Zodi</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>・The log-in bonus will be sent to you every day after 6:00 AM when you log in.</div><div>・Gifts sent as log-in bonuses can only be accepted for a limited time.</div><div>・The 5★ wyrmprint &quot;Second Anniversary&quot; will be gifted directly to players instead of being sent to their goodie boxes.</div><div><br></div><hr><div>6. The Forgotten Truths Raid Event is Coming!</div><div>The truths of a thousand years past are waiting to be revealed! Don&#39;t miss this limited-time raid event. Take on event-specific quests to defeat the raid boss with no elemental attunement and earn rewards!</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601445600"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1602482399"></span></div><div><br></div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/1626">See here for more information.</a></div><div><br></div><hr><div>7. The Alberian Battle Royale Debuts!</div><div>Up to 16 players battle for survival in this all-new battle-royale mode!</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601002800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1604123999"></span></div><div><br></div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/1624">See here for more information.</a></div><div><br></div><hr><div>8. 2nd Anniversary Stickers</div><div>Stickers themed after the 2nd Anniversary will be added at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601186400"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>To see the new stickers, select Player Info under Menu at the top of the screen in-game, then select Stickers and see the Available Stickers section. If you want to use the new stickers, please edit your Sticker Loadout, which is also under Stickers.</div><div><br></div><hr><div>9. Resetting the Social Reward in Co-op!</div><div>We will reset the number of times players can obtain the social reward, which can be obtained by playing co-op with another player for the first time, at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601013600"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>After clearing a quest, you can get 50 wyrmite per player (up to 50 times). You can get a total of 2,500, so be sure to play co-op!</div><div><br></div><hr><div>10. 2nd Anniversary Upgrade Events!</div><div>Starting at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601186400"></span>, a triple drops event for Avenue to Power and a triple rupies event for Avenue to Fortune will be held alongside many other events such as double drops for Advanced Dragon Trials and The Agito Uprising.</div><div><br></div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/1608">See here for more information.</a></div><div><br></div><hr><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1601002800,update_time1600944772